text: Anna Kalinskaya and Tereza Mihalíková were the defending champions, but both players were ineligible to participate. Bianca Andreescu and Carson Branstine won the title, defeating Maja Chwalińska and Iga Świątek in the final, 6–1, 7–6(7–4). == Seeds == == Draw == === Finals === === Top half === === Bottom half === == References == *Draw Girls' Doubles Australian Open, 2017 Girls' Doubles
